flowchart TD
    ORIGINATED["Loans Originated<br/>100,000 orders<br/>$20M total GMV<br/>Average order: $200"]

    ORIGINATED --> PERFORMING["Performing Loans<br/>~92-95% of originations<br/>Payments on schedule"]
